HEADWORD: Kshatruya
<hw>Ksha"tru*ya</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr.
<ets>kshatriya</ets> one belonging to the military caste.]</ety>
<def>The military caste, the second of the four great Hindu castes;
also, a member of that caste. See <er>Caste</er>.</def>
<mark>[India]</mark>⟦br⟧
